Application server is a server which has full support for JavaEE specification.

Web server is a server which supports subset of application server features.



Web server                        Application server

Servlets                          Servlets
JSP                               JSP
EL                                EL
WebSocket                         WebSocket
JTA                               JTA
JASPIC                            EJB
                                  CDI
                                  JMS
                                  JavaMail
                                  JAX-WS
                                  JAX-RS
                                  Bean Validation
                                  JSON-P


Web servers:
Apache Tomcat, Jetty, Undertow

Application servers:
Apache TomEE, Oracle WebLogic, WebSphere, WildFly, GlassFish
